Summary: Strange metallic oval object with a triangular structure on top.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting on the Banzai Pipeline Beach in Haleiwa taking pictures of the surfers and the waves. When I took a picture of the sun behind the palm tree, I did not notice the object. I only saw it once I loaded the picture in the computer. There was no noise of helicopter or plane as I took the picture. You are specialist, maybe you can tell me what it is. Thank you in advance
